OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FParents will be entitled to
OL,8,Fbereavement leave if they lose a
OL,9,Fpregnancy before 24 weeks, under new
OL,10,Fplans to be unveiled by the Government.
OL,12,FMinisters are set to amend the
OL,13,FEmployment Rights Bill so that people
OL,14,Fwill be entitled to protected time off
OL,15,Fin the event of a pregnancy loss,
OL,16,Fregardless of the stage at which it
OL,17,Fhappens.
OL,19,FAngela Rayner has said that the change
OL,20,Fwill give "people time away from work
OL,21,Fto grieve".
