OL,4,Cweeks to be entitled to bereavement
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FUnder current rules, parents are
OL,8,Fentitled to up to two weeks of
OL,9,Fbereavement leave if a child dies
OL,10,Fbefore they turn 18, or they
OL,11,Fexperience a stillbirth after 24 weeks
OL,12,Fof pregnancy.
OL,14,FAmendments to the Employment Rights
OL,15,FBill, will see the right to "at least
OL,16,Fone week's leave" expanded to people
OL,17,Fwho lose a pregnancy before 24 weeks.
OL,18,FThe exact length of the leave will be
OL,19,Fspecified in later legislation after a
OL,20,Fconsultation.
