OL,7,FThe Bill already makes provision to
OL,8,Fexpand bereavement leave, giving
OL,9,Femployees protected time off to grieve
OL,10,Fthe loss of a loved one.
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,13,Fhas said that the amendments will
OL,14,Foffer "dignity and respect".
