OL,7,F"For many families, including mine,
OL,8,Fthat have been affected by pregnancy
OL,9,Floss, the decision around returning to
OL,10,Fwork or taking sick leave to grieve
OL,11,Fproperly can make an already painful
OL,12,Fexperience even more difficult," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Grief doesn't follow a timetable, and
OL,16,Fexpanding rights to leave for
OL,17,Fpregnancy loss will ensure every
OL,18,Ffamily gets the time they need to heal
OL,19,Fwithout worrying about their job."
