OL,7,FDeputy Prime Minister Ms Rayner
OL,8,Fsimilarly said that "no-one who is
OL,9,Fgoing through the heartbreak of
OL,10,Fpregnancy loss should have to go back
OL,11,Fto work before they are ready".
OL,13,F"I am proud that this Government is
OL,14,Fintroducing a day-one right to
OL,15,Fprotected time off work after
OL,16,Fexperiencing pregnancy loss, giving
OL,17,Fpeople time away from work to grieve
OL,18,Fand spend time with their families,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
