OL,7,FVicki Robinson, chief executive of the
OL,8,FMiscarriage Association, welcomed the
OL,9,Fannouncement, saying it was "a hugely
OL,10,Fimportant step that acknowledges the
OL,11,Foften very significant impact of pre-
OL,12,F24-week loss, not only for those
OL,13,Fexperiencing the physical loss, but
OL,14,Ffor their partners too".
OL,16,FIt comes after ministers announced
OL,17,Fthey would review the system of
OL,18,Fparental leave, declaring that the
OL,19,Fcurrent system is "not working" for
OL,20,Ffamilies.
